snippet.title: SupraDarky
snippet.description:
A channel mostly about video game music, one of the most important parts of a game and certainly for me the best and fastest way to fall back into nostalgia for a game you loved.

So sit back, have a drink and enjoy! Comments and subscriptions are all welcome!

THIS LIST IS IN NO ORDER AT ALL!

---------------------------------------

*Project creation* 09/02/07
